            "Card not recognized": `<span class="important-note">Requirements:</span><br>- A customer reports their new debit card is not working. Upon checking, the transaction history (IST) shows:<br>- Transactions are available only from non-CIB ATMs.<br>- No transaction attempts are visible from CIB ATMs.<br>- TAT 2 WD<br><span class="important-note">NOTE:</span><br>- A replacement card will be issued for free.`,
