            "Cards Delivery Request-Account": `<span class="important-note">Requirements:</span><br>- 1-Validate card Exedit TAT or not ( Al TAT in Not )<br>- 2-Get Shipment number <br>- 3-start search On DCU sheet <br>- 4-If you didn't find any result So refer back to Courier Linke If you See (Undeliverd - Intranset …....)<br>- 5-OR if you see IN DCU ( Delivery Task ) so Search with the DCU refernce ( New Policy ) in the courier link before assigning Delivery Task to make Sure Card didn't deliverd <br>- 6-All instractions On DCU sheet Just follow The steps <br><span class="important-note">NOTE:</span><br>- TAT For Delivery Task<br>- Premium Cards  ( Platinum  ) New & Replacment 2 WD inside Cairo/ 4 WD outside<br>- Core ( Any card without Platinum  ) New & Replacement 5 WD inside Cairo / 7 WD outside<br>- Normal TAT for Delivery ( When the card issued ) the same this TAT but If card Renewal All Cards 15 WD `,
