            "SMS Alert Serv. Not Active-ACC": `<span class="important-note">Requirements:</span><br>- 1-Customer has their registered mobile number<br>- 2-Check SMS History in CRM:<br>- *If SMS appears in history (even with delivery status ""False"") → No action needed<br>- Bank system has sent the SMS, so issue is not from bank side<br>- *If SMS does NOT appear in history:<br>- Assign SMS Alert SR in CRM<br>- Open SD ticket directly<br>- Attach screenshot from CRM's SMS history tab showing no message found on transaction date<br><span class="important-note">NOTE:</span><br>- Request is assigned when a customer did not receive SMS alerts for their last 3 transactions<br>- Key Point: Only proceed with investigation when SMS is completely missing from the system history.`,
