            "Inactive Account": `<span class="important-note">Requirements:</span><br>- Receive & Verify Call: The call must be from the customer's registered mobile number.<br>- Validate Customer Data: The agent must check the following:<br>- Customer has a valid ID.<br>- Customer has another active account with the bank.<br>- Customer's KYC is valid.<br>-  (TAT): Same Day.<br><span class="important-note">NOTE:</span><br>- Take Action:<br><br>- If all validations are met: The agent activates the account in the T24 system (maker level) and then submits a request in the CRM for supervisor authorization.<br>- If any validation fails (invalid ID, no active account, or invalid KYC): The agent must apologize to the customer and advise them to visit the nearest branch.<br>- Escalate for Authorization: After creating the CRM request, the agent must immediately send the Service Request (SR) number to the Contact Center Operation Supervisors email group to be processed.`,
            "New Billing Cycle": `<span class="important-note">Requirements:</span><br>- If Customer has EPP it will be cancelled<br>- •Account Arrears level not exceed 30 days<br>- •Cannot apply on flagged account with override code<br>- •Can not apply to change between network Visa or Master or Vice Versa<br>- •Cannot apply in corporate products<br>- •Account agreement status should be 09 active card<br>- •Cannot apply for special products such as (Egypt Air – World –  Swype –  NooN – Cashback )<br>- •Cannot apply when old expiry date is less than 6 months <br>- No amounts on hold ( Hold to be released first to apply for the request )<br>-New Annual Fees will be applied.<br><span class="important-note">NOTE:</span><br>- Note :Any existing EPP will be cancelled when changing billing cycle <br>- Note2 :Credit Cards Billing Cycle:<br>-02   End of Month Date 30   Due Date   27 <br>-03   End of Month Date  30  Due Date    25<br>-08   End of Month Date  10  Due Date     5<br>-09   End of Month Date  20 Due Date   15<br>-10   End of Month Date 30 Due Date   15<br>-11  End of Month Date  30 Due Date   25<br>-15   End of Month Date 30 Due Date   15 <br>-13   End of Month Date  30 Due Date   10 `,
